markets.title: Dallas Vs Philadelphia: Combo
markets.yes_sub_title: Dallas Wins, Over 47.5 points scored, and CeeDee Lamb TD
markets.no_sub_title: Dallas Wins, Over 47.5 points scored, and CeeDee Lamb TD
markets.rules_primary: If Dallas is the winner in the Dallas at Philadelphia professional football game originally scheduled for Sep 4, 2025, the teams in the Dallas at Philadelphia professional football game originally scheduled for Sep 4, 2025 collectively score more than 47.5 points, and CeeDee Lamb scores a touchdown in Dallas at Philadelphia professional football game originally scheduled for Sep 4, 2025 then the market resolves to Yes.
markets.rules_secondary: If this game is postponed or delayed, the market will remain open and close after the rescheduled game has finished (within two weeks). If the cancelled game is not played or is rescheduled further than two weeks out, the market will resolve to a fair price for each team in accordance with the rules. If the game is declared a tie, the market will resolve to No. All three individual conditions (Game Outcome, Total Points, and Player Touchdown) must be met in order for this market to resolve Yes.
markets.early_close_condition: This market will close and expire early if the event occurs.
